"""Module to interact with data models.

This module contains class to interact with a data model in EMS data integration.

Typical usage example:

```python
data_model = data_pool.get_data_model(
    data_model_id
)
data_model.name = (
    "NEW_NAME"
)
data_model.update()
data_model.reload()
data_model.delete()
```
"""

